<subSubSection pageId="279" pageNumber="884" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="279.[1441,2646,728,1467]" pageId="279" pageNumber="884">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1443,1795,1318,1347]" pageId="279" pageNumber="884">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Vernay’s Climbing Mouse seems not to be affected by human activities.
